{"tid":1982873,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明：黃色經濟圈有害無利","createTime":"2020-04-21T12:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T02:41:04.000Z","uid":204401,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae0f4276aedd7d1515fdff707757a73f5c5252d","tid":1982873,"uid":204401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:34:44.000Z","msg":"香港教育大學社會學系講師黎明認為，餐廳的行為是一種政治表態，對自身保障和公眾防疫有害無益。她在其臉書貼文中寫道，「病毒不會以語言、地域身份或政治立場來區別傳染，在一場波及全球的疫情之中，任何人都有可能成為病毒攜帶者。把病毒和某個特定的群體關聯起來，讓我們誤以為只要驅逐、隔離了那個特定的群體，就可令自己更安全，結果反而對真正的風險視而不見、掉以輕心。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjcLLzt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjcLLzt.png&h=ec042e8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-51557050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-51557050&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=81b3d8b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-51557050</a>"},{"pid":"d4f5312d183fce2ac090f45c1db656bc03c11909","tid":1982873,"uid":204401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:38:26.000Z","msg":"黎明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c2e894c292f2bff07f523eafcbaeedcffcb8ee","tid":1982873,"uid":60120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:38:40.000Z","msg":"香港教育大學社會學系講師黎明認為，餐廳的行為是一種政治表態，對自身保障和公眾防疫有害無益<br />\n=<br />\n黃色經濟圈有害無利?"},{"pid":"00c7eaa4f2fbe3f9d07687a7c3a3311fc736c6ee","tid":1982873,"uid":204401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"奶共港師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd11a38cc49e05ae46f968ea88f40b29c788f64","tid":1982873,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c7eaa4f2fbe3f9d07687a7c3a3311fc736